Class FT_Coverage

  • Object
    • AbstractFeature
      • FT_Coverage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFeature

    public class FT_Coverage
extends AbstractFeature
    FT_Coverage is used to store image data (i.e. geotiffs). It stores the image itself as a Geotools GridCoverage and the envelope of this image. This class is intended to be a temporary class until the 2dCoverages are fully managed.
    Author:
    Bertrand Dumenieu
    See Also:
    GridCoverage2D
